Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:23.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:34.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう言って彼女はうつむいてたんだ　夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:41.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷たく貼り付いて　凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:48.86,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降り続く現実に　傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:55.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生きてゆくことが　戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:59.33,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな理由だけで　閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:02.22,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Heart　My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:09.71,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:16.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小さな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:23.16,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah  ah　鳥のように　飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:34.64,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませたとき　感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:36.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:42.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:23.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在伤害别人之前　不必强颜欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:34.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说着她低下头　在黑夜里哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:41.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷粘合在一起　浑身僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:48.86,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨下个不停　却没有伞来遮挡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:55.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己囚禁在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:59.33,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有战斗才能求生的因果之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:02.22,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心　我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:09.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪水的彼岸所见到的　是五彩光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:16.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的窗口　映照出那时蔚蓝的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:23.16,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　虽说不能像鸟儿一样自由翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:34.64,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害别人之后的那份心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:36.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不忘却
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:42.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻地闭上眼　哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:55.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}#22  为了未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.28,0:00:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚·修亨伯格制造出Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  制造出GN Drive的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武力介入只是布局
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.30,0:00:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引导人类走向革新
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我…要进行变革
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.16,0:00:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你所追求的极致么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being  再次出现…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.71,0:00:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次请务必给我与之战斗的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所追求的是作为战斗者所能到达的极致
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那少年曾说我扭曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我就是个只能与他战斗的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才期望着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取得这极致的胜利！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.99,0:01:17.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只期望胜利吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其它的么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用问？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接着未来的明天！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格杀勿论！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空手夺白刃？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战…战斗吧  少年…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲手把我劈开  并抓住这胜利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不给我最后一击？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着抓住明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了活着而战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈  路易斯·哈莱维的机体呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有反应  好像已经撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:02:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:02:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是突然想这么说而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为纯种而觉醒了么？  刹那·F·清荣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是掌握人类命运的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说知道吠陀所在的地方了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是来自王留美的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到吠陀了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加密信息解析完成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点是CZ9842R  是月球的背面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜  用超望远摄像头观测一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉格朗日2…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连殖民地开发都没有开始进行的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为隐藏地点相当不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将目标地点图像表示在显示器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个位置的星图和画面重叠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星的位置有所偏移
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是光学迷彩…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把偏离的距离算出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离是  直…直径15千米
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有15千米？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有那么大的东西藏在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在月球的背面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  实验室的运输舰发来加密通信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新装备来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独立治安维持部队A-LAWS\N将用全部战力进行对Celestial Being的歼灭作战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将作为反政府势力最后堡垒的他们打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢得统一世界的真正和平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待着诸位的奋战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,21艘巡洋舰和108台MS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么多的战力的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将  那些有特殊许可的家伙离开舰队了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管他们  就算他们在战场上乱来也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李本兹发来的返回命令…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他终于下决心了么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  跟计划一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为即将到来的东西迫在眉睫了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯·哈莱维…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人的仇？  我也有啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为不幸的只有自己吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活该…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们把能成为战力的东西都带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam各机的强化部件及托勒密的补给物资…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连O Gundam都带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为装上了粒子储藏设备  能进行一定时间的战斗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！  赶快搬进去！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美指定的地点有舰队在集结
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错了  吠陀就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改革者的总部也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破A-LAWS舰队并夺回吠陀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是场前所未有的激战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去吧  为了进行我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛斯劳德君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定了  不会再迷茫了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我也参加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏摩·佩丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有这么做的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  即使目的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都有各自前往那里的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.37,0:08:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  这些想法都连接着未来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了未来而战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了把人类从改革者的支配下解放出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了世界上不再出现像我或者苏摩·佩丽丝这样的存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒联邦政府是我的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狙击改革者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不改变的话  就不会有未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成补给之后  托勒密就立刻出发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  现在的托勒密还少一个舵手…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在这里么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身体能行么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然能行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到月球的背面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜殿下  有好多星星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢  非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  都注意下举止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS正在拉格朗日2集结舰队？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来自GIN1的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being好像也准备前往那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政变派那边也传来了相同的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还带有详细的战术计划…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配置完成  上校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了进行审判的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是作为纯种变革的刹那·F·清荣还是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟哪一方将决定人类前进的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拭目以待吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓武士道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是寻求死亡之道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了活着而战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓武士道…
