Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
