Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她不是那种关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去Gundam那边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死啊  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密  所有舱门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何也要夺回吠陀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请为我指引方向…  洛克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃德先生  期待你的战果！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:24.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee  特瑞亚·埃德  出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗  苏摩·佩丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我玛丽就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:38.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想这么叫的话  就这么叫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Archer-Arios  阿里路亚·哈普提兹姆  苏摩·佩丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驶向目标！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim  出击准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:13:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚琉  我会战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim  洛克恩·斯托拉托斯  狙击目标！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题吧  沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想找到自己的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解  OO  刹那·F·清荣  出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Raiser  沙慈·克洛斯罗德  出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗  O-Raiser对接模式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Raiser  对接模式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam从宇宙船中出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先头部队开始攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊任务舰  给我好好干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去牵制敌人部队！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压缩粒子  全面开放！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真行啊  这新装备
