Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特攻吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  用Raiser Sword阻击敌舰！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Raiser系统  启动！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM Raiser！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想扰乱粒子吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-Field大范围展开！
