Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:16:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好没让他们在近距离展开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变轨道  离开Field！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方的反应比我想象的要快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主力部队开始攻击  凭数量压倒他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  粒子光束无效！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹所剩不多了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人数量太多了！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷中弹！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损伤情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  想折磨死我们吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌机接近！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们终于来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塔隆！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩护Celestial Being！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援军？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塔隆吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机正好！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塔隆的武装…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是预测到有Anti-Field吗  这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将托勒密转向敌方舰队！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  卡塔隆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭他们的战力… 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将  我方的运输舰有异样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运输舰？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子光束发射过来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劝告A-LAWS舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们奋起反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沦为联邦恶政之傀儡的A-LAWS已非军队！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界前进的方向只应遵从于市民的合意而决定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现将汝等之暴行定罪  以向市民问求是非
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个狐狸精…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.73,0:19:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击溃他们！ 那是反政府势力！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方部队接近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS队  开始攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死之身的克拉萨乌  参上！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区一艘运输舰都搞不定  你们在干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们躲在僚舰后面  无法攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能动的己方留着有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不分敌友全都给我打下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是里面还有我方的士兵！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管了  给我射击！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将！ 敌舰突破Anti-Field了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G…Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO-Raiser  驱逐目标！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给…给我想想办法！
